        "---\n",
        "title: \"Consumer Complaint Analytics — Bank of America\"\n",
        "description: \"A Voting Classifier achieving 86.1% precision on 61,022 CFPB complaints, deployed as a live Streamlit dashboard with projected net savings of $470,500 and an ROI of 1,191%.\"\n",
        "author: \"Ruairí Cullen\"\n",
        "date: \"2024-12-01\"\n",
