        "categories: [Machine Learning, NLP, Python, Streamlit, Prescriptive Analytics]\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## Overview\n",
        "\n",
        "This project transforms Bank of America's complaint management from a slow reactive \n",
        "First-In-First-Out system into an AI-powered fast-track routing system. Using 61,022 \n",
        "real complaints from the Consumer Financial Protection Bureau (CFPB), a Voting Classifier \n",
        "combining Histogram-based Gradient Boosting and Random Forest achieves **86.1% precision** \n",
        "identifying complaints likely to require monetary relief.\n",
        "\n",
        "::: {.callout-tip}\n",
        "🚀 **Live Dashboard:** [analysisofcomplaints.streamlit.app](https://analysisofcomplaints.streamlit.app)\n",
        ":::\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## Key Results\n",
        "\n",
        "| Metric | Result |\n",
        "|---|---|\n",
        "| Model | Voting Classifier (Gradient Boosting + Random Forest) |\n",
        "| Precision | 86.1% |\n",
        "| ROC-AUC | 0.794 |\n",
        "| Accuracy | 77.4% |\n",
        "| Dataset Size | 61,022 CFPB complaints |\n",
        "| Projected Gross Savings | $510,000 |\n",
        "| Operational Cost | $39,500 |\n",
        "| **Net Benefit** | **$470,500** |\n",
        "| **ROI** | **1,191%** |\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## Feature Engineering\n",
        "\n",
        "The pipeline engineered the following features from raw CFPB data:\n",
        "\n",
        "- **TF-IDF vectorisation** of complaint Issue text (unigrams + bigrams, 1,000 features)\n",
        "- **Temporal features** — Days_to_Forward, Month_Sin, Month_Cos, Day_of_Week, Quarter\n",
        "- **Risk rate features** — Product_Risk_Rate, State_Risk_Rate (historical payout probabilities)\n",
        "- **Text metadata** — Issue_Length, Issue_Word_Count\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
